ini-kill">Bikini Kill</a> 、 <a href="/artists/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a> 、 <a href="/artists/kali-uchis">Kali Uchis</a> 、 <a href="/artists/zach-de-la-rocha">Zack de la Rocha</a> 、 <a href="/artists/tom-morello">Tom Morello</a> 、 <a href="/artists/brian-eno">Brian Eno</a> 、 Arooj Aftab 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blonde-redhead">Blonde Redhead</a> 、 <a href="/artists/kehlani">Kehlani</a> 、 <a href="/artists/denzel-curry">Denzel Curry</a> 、 Pink Siifu 、 Mica Levi 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lrain">L&#39;Rain</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/laurel-halo">月桂光环</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deerhoof">鹿蹄</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-ditto">贝丝·迪托</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-knife">刀的奥洛夫·德雷耶</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mykki-blanco">米基·布兰科</a>、圣母、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/youth-lagoon">青春泻湖</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fucked-up">搞砸了</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mogwai">莫格瓦伊</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bonnie-prince-billy">邦妮“王子”比利</a>、Kode9、维杰·艾耶、埋葬陌生人的地方、尼古拉斯·贾尔、埃拉多·内格罗、Raffi、KeiyaA、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mandy-indiana">Mandy Indiana</a>等等。</p><p>这封信是娱乐界最新的停火呼吁。本月早些时候，由前工党领袖杰里米·科尔宾创立的<a href="http://bit.ly/MusicForACeasefire" target="_blank" rel="noopener">和平与正义项目</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/enter-shikari-the-last-dinner-party-architects-and-more-sign-open-letter-for-music-for-a-ceasefire-3536081">于 11 月 10 日发布了艺术家、音乐家和表演者的#MusicForACeasefire 公开信，“呼吁结束对加沙的围困”</a> 。</p><p>这封信还得到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enter-shikari">《Enter Shikari</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">《最后的晚宴》、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/architects">《建筑师》、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">《英语老师》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-blessed-madonna">《圣母》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/king-gizzard-and-the-lizard-wizard">《吉扎德国王和蜥蜴巫师》等</a>艺术家的签名，呼吁“立即在加沙停火并停止对加沙的轰炸”。巴勒斯坦已经夺走了一万多名无辜平民、援助人员和记者的生命。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">The Libertines</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fontaines-dc">Fontaines DC</a>是上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-the-libertines-and-more-sign-gaza-music-for-a-ceasefire-letter-3539045">最新签署和平与正义项目公开信的音乐家</a>。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cz1TW5CtDVv/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,