are Beauty 宣布将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/selena-gomez-makeup-brand-to-donate-funds-to-the-gaza-relief-efforts-3534155">救援工作捐款在加沙。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tilda-swinton-steve-coogan-and-massive-attacks-robert-del-naja-among-2000-artists-calling-for-gaza-ceasefire-in-open-letter-3516616">来自艺术界的 2000 多名人士</a>，包括蒂尔达·斯文顿 (Tilda Swinton)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>的罗伯特·德尔·纳贾 (Robert Del Naja) 和米里亚姆·马戈伊尔斯 (Miriam Margoyles) 签署了一封公开信，呼吁停火。</p><p>同样，麦当娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-on-israel-hamas-conflict-how-can-human-beings-be-so-cruel-to-one-another-3518887">也谈到了 O2 舞台上的情况</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benefits">贝里斯</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/benefits-share-powerful-statement-on-armistice-day-and-the-israel-palestine-war-3536251">就正在进行的以色列-哈马斯战争以及上周五（11 月 10 日）停战日发表了一份强有力的声明</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-morello-says-theres-no-room-for-anti-semitism-when-criticising-horrific-war-crimes-in-gaza-3537940">汤姆·莫雷洛最近表示，在批评“加沙的可怕战争罪行”时，“没有反犹太主义的余地”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-and-lucy-dacus-among-thousands-of-musicians-to-have-signed-letter-for-gaza-ceasefire-3546651">纸浆 (Pulp) 和露西·达库斯 (Lucy Dacus) 是数千名签署加沙停火信的音乐家之一，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
